{"tid":1935762,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[正視聽］其實根本唔存在Chinese呢個ethnicity","createTime":"2020-03-20T19:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T01:01:24.000Z","uid":21460,"like":54,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6bbec14933e0176a2a941bb37ad391a7620a2574","tid":1935762,"uid":21460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T19:18:22.000Z","msg":"見到唔少手足喺twitter戰線都會以自已係ethnically Chinese但唔覺得受冒犯，去backup &ldquo;Chinese virus&rdquo;之說，所以突登開個post講下。<br />\n<br />\n依家坊間所講嘅ethnically Chinese，大多指中文所講嘅「華人」。 中華民族呢個概念只係梁啟超喺政權交替時提出嘅新概念，想比起西方各種嘅民族主義，中華民族只不過係將舊政權（清政府）屬土內嘅唔同種族嘅百姓全數歸納為「華人」，目的係要避免少數民族嘅獨立，確保新政權可以繼承到所有領土。正如孫大炮一開始主張驅除躂虜，但掌權後又提倡五族共和，所謂「中華民族」呢個只不過係政治操作嘅一種，從來都只係政權嘅工具。<br />\n<br />\n開埠之今，香港已經發展出自己嘅民族性，完全無需以「華人」自居。除咗話自己係Hongkonger之外，退而求其次話自己嘅ethnicity係asian都絕對比Chinese好。<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇小呢啲嘢，其實正正係呢啲雞毛蒜皮嘅事先幫到香港人建構正確嘅民族意識，光復香港嘅一小步就係由呢啲小事開始。"},{"pid":"4f52e1ae03cfac839dc26165ccdc31e95823d179","tid":1935762,"uid":270889,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T19:31:00.000Z","msg":"讀讀孫文的「民族主義」，如何洗腦你當個「堂堂正正的中國人」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/26487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F26487&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=a1d0ad0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/26487</a><br />\n<br />\n我成日都講本身咩華人/中華民族只係洗腦term<br />\n係咁易數都漢滿蒙回藏 仲有大撚把minorities未數<br />\n最明顯嘅就係Uygurs<br />\n人地就係唔覺自己係你咩鳩野中華民族一份子<br />\n就比支共捉入去洗腦屠殺<br />\n<br />\n見到班白左盲反侵講Chinese Virus is racist<br />\n就一定同佢講Chinese is not even a race/ethnicity<br />\n咁撚大愛又唔見你幫Uygurs出多幾句聲<br />\n<br />\nburnhill 大中華膠反省系列都有好詳細咁講"},{"pid":"86c67c8dc7625ea25004d395e9ace4f79255dc5f","tid":1935762,"uid":21460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T19:39:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6dcdcc7a54d408913f13f0bb786899d86247a31c","tid":1935762,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T19:52:17.000Z","msg":"根本上分黃人，白人，黑人，中東人就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea0ceaf245e093547f2f2495d7d13e1fa872889","tid":1935762,"uid":303794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T20:01:35.000Z","msg":"Cantonese"},{"pid":"804dd1f7f7d5073284a55ab26b6e49f14b78f839","tid":1935762,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T20:24:53.000Z","msg":"漢人得喇掛"},{"pid":"ff755adf5491dc7a11345b1ae8565c0e3fd270f9","tid":1935762,"uid":170229,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T21:21:45.000Z","msg":"應該畫個poland ball, 用starwar you killed my father 做meme, 然後就係中國每次被入侵後就認賊作父。"},{"pid":"99f025076c4ec5ae5359220ba66c90e0c33c9a91","tid":1935762,"uid":165773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"804dd1f7f7d5073284a55ab26b6e49f14b78f839","tid":1935762,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T20:24:53.000Z","msg":"漢人得喇掛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T21:41:30.000Z","msg":"「漢人」係因應政治需要而隨意捏造嘅詞語 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/773798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/773798</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"80196549536b94aa0cc6d9fb67e84b9bcfa5e4da","tid":1935762,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"804dd1f7f7d5073284a55ab26b6e49f14b78f839","tid":1935762,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T20:24:53.000Z","msg":"漢人得喇掛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T21:53:39.000Z","msg":"咁樣我諗大部分香港人都唔係漢人"},{"pid":"e8e44162e1ec513df76321ba752ef93a634515e2","tid":1935762,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T21:53:40.000Z","msg":"Fuck the Chinese<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23546463ff5a51a0c52190cba4a3c4b6cf5a9503","tid":1935762,"uid":345819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T21:54:37.000Z","msg":"Race嘅話就粵人，照鏡都睇到同平頭細眼北佬唔同<br />\n當然都有啲香港人係北方種，不過身邊識嘅係大眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nEthnicity我覺得有好多討論空間，如果睇傳統文化呢啲可以話自己廣東人Cantonese，不過都有啲人提倡用Hongkongese，因為已經同大陸文化拉到好大分別<br />\nNationality呢個唔洗諗，希望有朝一日入境紙名正言順填Hongkongese，香港獨立唯一出路"},{"pid":"1b4f8d548a6b32dd2ca670ee4e6643ce54f41a72","tid":1935762,"uid":157411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T21:59:18.000Z","msg":"話自己係Chinese係想塞住班白人左膠把口呀<br />\n你估好撚想認自己係Chinese架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f921c09e960afbac30a8d3fca810d4629f61ea7","tid":1935762,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T22:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c942c5203fcaf7c83ac21473c2be65dd226ff4f","tid":1935762,"uid":326017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80196549536b94aa0cc6d9fb67e84b9bcfa5e4da","tid":1935762,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"804dd1f7f7d5073284a55ab26b6e49f14b78f839","tid":1935762,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T20:24:53.000Z","msg":"漢人得喇掛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T21:53:39.000Z","msg":"咁樣我諗大部分香港人都唔係漢人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T22:17:19.000Z","msg":"秦人？定越人"},{"pid":"bb7c99180a58f9709f50560b9ed454cc6606c6b6","tid":1935762,"uid":261773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T22:18:09.000Z","msg":"美國自古以來都是英國固有領土 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國唔係一個國家，因為佢地流著英國人嘅血 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca5e6303da3dad167a167c720ecf55111e284e0","tid":1935762,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T23:15:53.000Z","msg":"算啦<br />\n加陣重點唔係我地唔識分<br />\n而係外國白人黑人唔識分而要打我地<br />\n身分分得仔細係有用<br />\n但係只係for有文化/腦嘅外國人<br />\n而打黃種人果班正正就係無腦無文化果班人<br />\n佢地點會咁得閒同你細分<br />\n幾多人連hong kong都唔知係邊<br />\n咁做係太平盛世可能有用<br />\n但依家呢個情況唔太得<br />\n<br />\n香港好多人仲未識醒<br />\n佢地要有一日有自己友係表明hkger身分後都比人打到仆街就會明<br />\n本身接觸外國人多<br />\n已經不下一大堆人同我講nihao<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌佢老味香港人講cantonese架<br />\n但真係好難解釋勁多人都係未明"},{"pid":"6434688b0bf5e00a5927fee708ba433e373461cc","tid":1935762,"uid":25164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T00:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b138de582c09c25d92cc628b19eb7499258bf935","tid":1935762,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T00:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d1943faca6f5626ea84fe47419323d59bcbde1","tid":1935762,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c942c5203fcaf7c83ac21473c2be65dd226ff4f","tid":1935762,"uid":326017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80196549536b94aa0cc6d9fb67e84b9bcfa5e4da","tid":1935762,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"804dd1f7f7d5073284a55ab26b6e49f14b78f839","tid":1935762,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T20:24:53.000Z","msg":"漢人得喇掛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T21:53:39.000Z","msg":"咁樣我諗大部分香港人都唔係漢人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T22:17:19.000Z","msg":"秦人？定越人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T00:57:05.000Z","msg":"越"},{"pid":"f96947ae2ce819a0d3fbc71ca3fb819e6f7669f5","tid":1935762,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T00:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a379178d8d55a83f7b5545ca53da75401749a144","tid":1935762,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy